<h1 align="center"><font face="Arial" size="7">&nbsp;How to use the Metrics?</font></h1>
<p><font face="Arial" size="6">Metrics help you</font></p>
<p>　</p>
<blockquote>
  <blockquote>
    <ul>
      <li><font face="Arial" size="6">achieve your goal on time, on budget</font></li>
    </ul>
    <p>　</p>
    <ul>
      <li><font face="Arial" size="6">reflect the status of your project as well 
      as plan for unforeseen and upcoming activities.</font></li>
    </ul>
    <p>　</p>
    <ul>
      <li><font face="Arial" size="6">influence what your team considers 
      important and what they do</font></li>
    </ul>
    <p>　</p>
    <ul>
      <li><font face="Arial" size="6">compare your progress against industry 
      standards</font></li>
    </ul>
    <p>　</p>
    <ul>
      <li><font face="Arial" size="6">assess where you stand and to show the 
      value of CBSE has to your organization by Quantitative and Objective Data&nbsp;
      </font></li>
    </ul>
  </blockquote>
</blockquote>

